name: Thank You, Mother
description:
Mother. I'm still a child at that time. I'm still learning life from you. So that our time is filled with more dazzling memories of us. I always try to see you and be with you.

Thank you, Mother. You've endlessly looked strong. You've had to turn around and endure things alone, I became old enough to know a little about that. I promise, I will do well.
